{"id":250744,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-福建侯文泉老人6年控告政府强拆难讨公道/","date":"2012-09-08T09:46:18Z","modified":"2012-09-08T09:46:18Z","title":"维权网 | 福建侯文泉老人6年控告政府强拆难讨公道（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span>（维权网信息员钟剑报道）福建省莆田涵江区国欢镇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">77</span><span>岁高龄的农民侯文泉，一生竟然遭遇到当地政府两次强拆。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>第一次是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年，其祖辈留下来的房产三处被强拆，补偿金仅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4300</span><span>元，而且不给予任何安置。走投无路的侯文泉从此踏上上访之路。第二次是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年，侯文泉家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>间住房被国欢镇政府强制拆除。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>眼看上访没有结果，侯文泉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年开始将国欢镇政府告上法庭。然而由于官官相护及利益纠葛，该案竟然在经过福建省高级法院、莆田市中院、涵江区法院累计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>次审判、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>次裁决之后仍然没有任何结果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>侯文泉老人经过漫长的上访、诉讼，目前正在期待第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>个判决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>侯文泉手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13850219719</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ysd0alNsToI/UEsOizT-SFI/AAAAAAAANrk/6FPHdjRWsiA/s1600/113168442.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ysd0alNsToI/UEsOizT-SFI/AAAAAAAANrk/6FPHdjRWsiA/s320/113168442.jpg\" width=\"142\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8244077980408554912?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com